      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CROSS LOCKS (6) caught the eye when posting an outstanding 21.98 over 390m at Shepparton three back then has hit the frame in both runs since. Should be in this for a long way. SWEET TRILBY (3) is struggling to break through but racing consistently, finishing in the minors three starts on end. Last time out flew the lids with a fast early sectional but gathered in and finished in the minors when third (26.22) at this track over 460m. Well placed and gets her chance. LENORA JAMES (1) turned in a modest effort most recently when sixth at this track over 460m behind Reality Ollie (26.52) in a Grade 5. Should be about the mark. STORM BREWING (2) is in winning form and worth including in the main hopes.",
